---

<Layout title="About Us | Vanchu Hut" description="Craving affordable Chinese food in Pratap Vihar? Discover popular Chinese dishes and delicious vegetarian options at Vanchu Hut.">
  <h1 class="hidden">Vanchu Hut - Affordable Chinese Food in Pratap Vihar, Ghaziabad</h1>
    <section class="py-12 bg-white-100 font-agdasima">
      <Image format="avif" src={heroImg} class="scale-100 w-screen h-[140px] transform -translate-y-[101px] md:-translate-y-[60px]  object-cover" alt="Decorative header - Vanchu Hut Chinese cuisine ambiance"/>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
        
        <!-- Welcome Section -->
  <section class=" bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary">
            Discover Affordable Chinese Food at Vanchu Hut in Pratap Vihar
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Welcome to Vanchu Hut, your go-to destination for delicious and affordable Chinese food in Pratap Vihar. Nestled in the heart of Ghaziabad, we pride ourselves on serving a variety of popular Chinese dishes that cater to every palate. Whether you‚Äôre craving classic favorites or innovative twists on traditional recipes, our menu is designed to delight both meat lovers and vegetarians alike.          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
