      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Join Us for an Authentic Chinese Dining Experience
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Come taste the difference that passion, tradition, and quality ingredients make.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/menu" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-white text-primary font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-300">
